ğŸŒ¸ Iris Flower Classification Web App

This project is a Flask web application that predicts the type of Iris flower (Setosa, Versicolor, Virginica) based on user inputs.
It uses a trained Machine Learning model (saved with joblib) and also visualizes prediction probabilities with bar and pie charts.

