âš™ï¸ Installation & Setup

Clone the repo:

git clone https://github.com/your-username/iris-flask-app.git
cd iris-flask-app


Install dependencies:

pip install flask joblib scikit-learn matplotlib numpy


Run the Flask app:

python app.py


Open in browser:

http://127.0.0.1:5000/

